{"type":"message","id":"4f3ccb79","parentId":"b44e733d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:50:00.893Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:71b19e21-52a4-446a-bc53-72399efd63f1 08:50全球股市早间要闻] 执行以下任务：\n1. 进入 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/news-market\n2. 运行 python3 scripts/generate_morning_news_free.py --output /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/global_market_morning_free_latest.md --json-output /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/global_market_morning_free_latest.json\n3. 读取上述 md/json 输出\n4. 用中文简短汇报：一句话总览、隔夜市场要点、大盘体温、A股开盘前结论、2-3条关键新闻与输出文件路径\n5. 本任务使用免费链路：Yahoo Search 主搜 + DuckDuckGo 兜底 + yfinance/akshare 数据\n6. 非交易时段不要给可执行买价，只给方向、优先级和触发条件\nCurrent time: Friday, April 3rd, 2026 — 8:50 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-03 00:50 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775177400887}}
